{"name":"Tower Game","stars":"4.5","desc":"The Tower Game is a custom-developed game. It's divided into several levels, each progressively more difficult. Each level features a tower of blocks. At the top of the tower is an object that must be carefully lowered without falling. This can be done by deleting or clicking on blocks. The game tracks your time during each level and displays the global overall best time at the end.","redirect":"https://jj-jetpack.github.io/Tower/","thumbnail":"<svg version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"433\" height=\"212\" viewBox=\"0,0,433,212\"><g transform=\"translate(-103.5,-74)\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"0\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M113.5,286c-5.52285,0 -10,-4.47715 -10,-10v-192c0,-5.52285 4.47715,-10 10,-10h413c5.52285,0 10,4.47715 10,10v192c0,5.52285 -4.47715,10 -10,10z\" fill=\"#00b745\"/><g><g><g><path d=\"M391.41798,169.58089v27.36788h-27.36788v-27.36788z\" fill=\"#ff5959\"/><path d=\"M362.50358,169.58089v27.36788h-114.03228v-27.36788z\" fill=\"#0001ff\"/></g><g><path d=\"M304.87467,141.49734v27.36789h-56.45477v-27.36789z\" fill=\"#f6ff00\"/><path d=\"M391.58012,141.49732v27.36789h-84.78988v-27.36789z\" fill=\"#00ff3c\"/></g><path d=\"M390.88234,112.45504v27.36788h-142.01307v-27.36788z\" fill=\"#ff00d7\"/></g><g><g><path d=\"M248.58204,225.14551v-27.36789h27.36788v27.36789z\" fill=\"#ff5959\"/><path d=\"M277.49644,225.14551v-27.36789h114.03228v27.36789z\" fill=\"#0001ff\"/></g><g><path d=\"M335.12535,253.22906v-27.36789h56.45477v27.36789z\" fill=\"#f6ff00\"/><path d=\"M248.4199,253.22907v-27.36789h84.78988v27.36789z\" fill=\"#00ff3c\"/></g><path d=\"M249.11768,282.27135v-27.36788h142.01307v27.36788z\" fill=\"#ff00d7\"/></g></g></g></g></svg>"}
